  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Place the lamb kidney in a small ramekin.",
    "Mix the olive oil, minced garlic, salt, and black pepper in a small bowl.",
    "Brush the mixture evenly over the lamb kidney.",
    "Place the Binchotan charcoal in a small metal tray or heat diffuser.",
    "Place the ramekin over the charcoal, creating a makeshift smoker.",
    "Close the oven door and smoke the lamb kidney for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the ramekin from the oven and sprinkle with chopped parsley and dill.",
    "Drizzle with lemon juice and serve immediately."
